---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
        <main class="main-content">
			<h1>üßë‚ÄçüöÄ Cleaving The Whole</h1>
			<p style="text-align: center">
                Where inquiry becomes illumination
			</p>
			<hr>
            <p class="intro">
                "To cleave is both to split and to adhere‚Äîin this paradox lies the path to understanding's deepest chambers."
            </p>

            <section class="archetype-description">
                <h2>The Archetype</h2>
                <p>Cleaving The Whole represents the sacred art of penetrating to the essential heart of any matter through multiple convergent paths of inquiry. Like a crystal that reveals its inner structure only when light strikes it from precise angles, truth emerges not from single-minded pursuit, but from the disciplined orchestration of diverse epistemological approaches.</p>

                <p>This archetype embodies the recognition that the most profound insights arise when we simultaneously split open our assumptions and cleave closely to rigorous methodology‚Äîwielding both the surgeon's precision and the mystic's intuition.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="principles">
                <div class="principle">
                    <h3>üîç Radical Inquiry</h3>
                    <p>Questioning not just the answers, but the questions themselves. Every assumption becomes a doorway to deeper investigation, every certainty an invitation to explore the foundations beneath.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="principle">
                    <h3>üåä Multi-Modal Approach</h3>
                    <p>Truth rarely yields to a single method. We employ analytical rigor alongside intuitive sensing, empirical observation coupled with contemplative insight, creating a symphony of understanding.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="principle">
                    <h3>‚öñÔ∏è Epistemological Integrity</h3>
                    <p>Maintaining unwavering commitment to intellectual honesty while remaining open to paradigm-shifting discoveries. The courage to follow evidence wherever it leads, even when it challenges our most cherished beliefs.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="principle">
                    <h3>üéØ Essential Distillation</h3>
                    <p>Cutting through layers of complexity and cultural conditioning to reach the irreducible core. Like a master jeweler who knows exactly where to strike the rough diamond to reveal its hidden brilliance.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="metaphor-section">
                <h2>The Way of the Cleaver</h2>
                <p class="metaphor-text">
                    Consider the master chef who knows that true cleaving requires understanding the grain of the meat, the temper of the blade, and the rhythm of the cut. So too, the seeker who would cleave reality must understand the grain of the question, temper their methods with wisdom, and find the natural rhythm where understanding flows effortlessly through resistance.
                </p>
            </section>

		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
body {
    font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #2c2c2c;
    // background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
    min-height: 100vh;
}

.container {
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    min-height: 100vh;
    box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}

header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #8b4513;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
}

h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: #2c1810;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #8b4513;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
}

.main-content {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.intro {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    color: #4a4a4a;
    font-style: italic;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.05);
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
}

.archetype-description {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}

.archetype-description h2 {
    color: #2c1810;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.principles {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
}

.principle {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.08);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 5px solid #8b4513;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.principle:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.principle h3 {
    color: #2c1810;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
}

.principle p {
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.metaphor-section {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.1), rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.05));
    border-radius: 12px;
}

.metaphor-section h2 {
    color: #2c1810;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
}

.metaphor-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #4a4a4a;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

.navigation {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
}

.nav-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 0 1rem;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    background: #8b4513;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    font-weight: 500;
}

.nav-link:hover {
    background: #a0522d;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.symbol {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #8b4513;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
</style>
